My brother - John, he died in the Edinburgh Castle, double pneumonia - 1804, that's when we were in Bellevue Road, he was a bandsman in the H.L.I. That's my father's regiment you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 And then after John was who, was he the eldest one?
