The same. A watchmaker, aye. Of course he was a bandsman the same as me you see And he was in the - 38}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\super\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432  regiment - infantry, he was a 
bandsman there. During the war. During - during the war, aye, that. But you had brassbands - before that you see. Town bands you see. Mor - Mor - Mordelachen and - I forget the names of them now. You - you had quite a few bands you see, you went - went fr
om one to another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 So there was you and Charlie and John?
