After the - oh no, just - working in shops - well he - he wasna working long, he - he - he - he joined the Army. He was a Scots Grace. But went as a bandboy the Scots Grace. And then - he went out to - he was in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}
Palestine{\*\xmlclose}, in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}India{\*\xmlclose} - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}India{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} 
a long time, and he transferred to the - the clerical corps or something. And he - he made a - I think they got a - protective stripe - corporal or something like that you see, then he - when the - when the regiment came home he - he came back with the re
giment you see, he had to leave that job you see, clerical job, and he came back and he was only - he took up - travelling for - traveller's job you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 Can you remember what sort of thing he travelled for?
