 was work - a - apprentice - dressmaker with St Culverts store. But - she didn't stick it long, about three or - three or four years. And she wasna there very long, she - she left - left the - dressmaking and - was just at home you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 Had she always been at home since?
