rmonium or the piano, our old piano, and - or - or the harmonium, and my brother'd be on the piano and I would be on the double bass and - some -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 What about Willie, did he play the clarinet or anything at that time?
