\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 You didn't get a row when you got home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7678773 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 No. I remember once going into - from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address
}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Glen Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} - a crowd, we went - went into Portobello, the summertime. And - I came back - my bare feet, I walked all the way Portobello in barefeet. I got - I g
ot a - I got a leathering for that. For - for coming with my barefeet.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 
Were you allowed to play with any children you liked or was there anyone that your parents said you're not to play with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7678773 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 No, no, we'll say no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 They didn't pick out people for you to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7678773 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7678773 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 
No. There was none - there was - as far as I remember there was - there was none in - except the Boys Brigade, there was one - I think there was only the 
Boys - I - I think there'd be a Boys Brigade in those days, I - I don't - I don't remember one though. I think there was. No, I don't think there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 
When you were at school you played in the street when you came home, did you have any hobbies as well, did you collect anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7678773 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 Stamps. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 Did you go for walks at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7678773 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 
Well the - the reason I started stamp collecting was - there was - a - an old chap lived on - blew the organ, you know, he pumped the organ - in the church you see, but
 - before they got the - hydraulic in, and it - San - Sandy Anderson was his name, an old man, and he - picked this - book up - out of bucket I expect, and he gave it to my father and it was a - a book of stamps. Just a - a small one you know. And - I've 
s
till got it. Aye. The - the - the stamps have been stuck on. See, they were stuck on. And - I've still got some of them stuck on yet, there's a - a - Bavarian or a - I don't know if they're valuable or not. They're Bavarian things you know. But I think th
ey were - I think they've been ruined with sticking them on. Aye, stuck on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 Did you ever go fishing or for walks?
