tors to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7678773 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 
No, you see, that - when we were in Bellevue Road, that was when I was - when I was - a young postman - assistant postman - they - used to - a surprise - what they call a surprise parties. People would come - a gang would come up -
 but they'd - they'd bring all the stuff with them. All provisions you see. For - for a - night - and - take - took over the house you see, and had a party in the house and - sing-song and that sort of thing. And they supplied all the grub you see.
\par 
