Well of course when I was at - when I went to Skerries I - I - I got in with two or three chaps and we - used to - I think I was due them about a - a dozen essays at the finish so
 they - of course they - they didna care. They were getting the money for it, you know, I was - and I didna carry on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6359732 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1794554\charrsid7551432 When you were at school did you ever have a part time job?
